title: A whisper from the depths calls
description: A whisper from the depths calls to you, adventurer. Seek the ancient secrets hidden at Waterfront Pier. There, among the weathered planks and salt-sprayed railings, you must decipher cryptic symbols etched into the wood, for they hold a truth long forgotten.

trailLocation.title: Waterfront Pier
trailLocation.description: A scenic waterfront pier perfect for strolling, fishing, and enjoying panoramic water views.
trailLocation.location: Carriage Path, Lake Buena Vista, FL 32830, United States of America
